lead_paragraph: South Korean Jang Ha-na made history with an albatross, as Swede Anna Nordqvist and English teenager Charley Hull earned a share of the third-round lead at the Pure Silk Bahamas LPGA Classic on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Jang Has Historic Albatross as Nordqvist, Hull Take LPGA Lead
